comments.body: The named export does seem to be wrong if I'm reading the [source](https://unpkg.com/axe-webdriverjs@2.3.0/dist/index.js) correctly... do you know what the deal is with that?

I believe it's left here after being added by original author:
https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/pull/26309/files
so because it works, it's untouched.
The original solution was probably to answer the problem:
https://github.com/dequelabs/axe-webdriverjs/issues/74
